@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Alternative Two

autonumber

actor "HRM" as Manager
participant ":System" as System

activate Manager

    Manager -> System : asks to generate a new Team
     activate System

        System --> Manager : show skills list/requests data (i.e. skills set)
     deactivate System

    Manager -> System : types requested data
     activate System

    alt Minimum >= 1
    System --> Manager : requests data ( max team size,\n min team size )
    end

    Manager -> System : types requested data
     activate System

    System --> Manager : shows all data and requests confirmation or modification
     deactivate System

    opt optional for "HRM"
    Manager -> System : modify data
     activate System

    System --> Manager : shows all data and requests confirmation or modification.
    deactivate System
    end

    Manager -> System : confirm the data
    activate System

        System --> Manager : displays operation success
    deactivate System
@enduml